page.html: [profile:1337][/profile:1337]Hello this is LawXiii, or just call me Law. I mostly plays 4k mode, sometime I did try 7k and 6k for fun, although I'm not good at both. I also play stepmania and SDO before started playing osumania few months ago. I'm quite newbie to this game, but I'll try to catch up with the others soon. I don't play 4 stars and below songs, unless the song is my favourite (in terms of listening) , so don't expect me to get many SS score in my profile because I only play the hard ones. I don't intend to spam those easy song just to get some extra PP. For fair reasons to pro players, I hope osu! approve more harder files (5 - 7 stars) for 4k into ranking song lists and stop approving too many 4 star and below anime songs.
